short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Autofill a new work on Ao3 or Squidgeworld

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
This extension helps you crosspost works from AO3 to AO3 clones, such as Squidgeworld. When you post a new work, this extension can help you by importing tags, rating, authors notes, and chapter content to match the work that you intend to crosspost.

This is an unofficial extension and not supported by AO3. Please do not raise issues with this extension to AO3 support.
